(although the pension already represents net income taxed through the translation of the gross pension 
basis to the net pension basis) and the wage income is subject to social security contributions. Whilst the 
contributions to pension insurance translate into a higher replacement rate upon full retirement, 
contributions for health and unemployment insurance act essentially as a tax since individuals who meet 
